<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b>Chairman of <a href="/wiki/National_Republican_Senatorial_Committee" title="National Republican Senatorial Committee">National Republican Senatorial Committee</a></b><br />
1991–1995</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Al_D%27Amato" title="Al D'Amato">Al D'Amato</a><br />
New York</b></td>
</tr>
